From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 01:24:35 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Support component-backed custom block behavior

- Route custom hardness, tool speed, and correct-tool checks through vanilla mining calculations while preserving enchantment and player-state modifiers.
- Replace vanilla player-break drops with the custom block item binding when one is configured.
- Preserve custom carrier states before block placement side effects can rewrite them.
- Suppress carrier attack, interaction, shape, and neighbor behavior unless the custom block explicitly inherits its base behavior.

